                <title>General Assembly Senate 117th Session Districts</title>
                <geoform>vector digital data</geoform>
            </citeinfo>
        </citation>
        <descript>
            <abstract>This dataset shows the boundaries of Indiana Senate Districts for the 117th General Assembly and provides the names and party affiliations of the legislators.District boundaries were provided to the Indiana Geological Survey (IGS) by the Indiana Election Division (IED). Personnel of the IGS added the names of legislators to the dataset, using information obtained from the official web site of the Indiana General Assembly (http://www.in.gov/legislative/ ).</abstract>
            <purpose>This shapefile was created to show the boundaries of Indiana Senate Districts for the 117th General Assembly.
It also provides the names and party affiliations of the legislators. This data was downloaded from maps.indiana.edu and republished by IGIO staff on 1/25/2023.</purpose>
        </descript>
